    description = Cyclical strategic framework for market dominance
    phases = DESTABILIZATION — weaken target's market position  | VECTOR MAPPING — identify path of least resistance | INFILTRATION — establish first foothold in target' | EXPANSION & CONTROL — deepen market access, establ | VALUE EXTRACTION — achieve primary objective: clie
    cycle_completion = Resources and intelligence from one cycle fuel DESTABILIZATION of the next target.
  motto = POWER IS NEVER GIVEN. IT IS TAKEN.

